<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>الأحول هو ابن أبي مسلم*<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>[<span class="c2">(٣٩١)</span> <span class="c2">(ع-سليمان)</span>]<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>الأعمش هو ابن مهران*<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>[<span class="c2">(٣٩٢)</span> <span class="c2">(ع-سليمان)</span>]<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>التيمي هو ابن طرخان*<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
